{
  "stem": "7781.4",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And every time, on each floor was a soldier who's supposed to be-- you're going to be quartered there, handing out cards.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "By the time we wound up on the fourth floor, we had four cards.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "These four cards were a bonanza, because they're food cards.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "In other words, you-- it was a mess hall.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "For four people.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And for four-- if they gave us cigarettes, I got for four people cigarettes.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And those cards were a bonanza, because I could eat four breakfasts, four lunches, four suppers.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I used to save the bread and eat at night, wake up in the middle of the night and eat a loaf of bread.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Like, the bread was white.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Beautiful, you know, and the food was good.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You know, the same English.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We had breakfast, you know, and then we had lunch, and tea time, and crumpets, and all those things.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They-- they fed us good.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "There where I regained strength.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And there where we met Jewish girls.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not girls like-- not what you have in mind.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We walked in the street, and we met three girls.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They were three Jewish German girls.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they lived on German [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] food rations, because they were German citizens.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They could--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we gave them cards.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We had three cards.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We gave our cards, and then we took them to camp.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We introduced them, that they are cousins.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was a-- it was a-- you know, you look at that like you [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "That was very important.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "To them, was food.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we supplied them with the cards, and they used to come and eat in the camp.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You know, you could walk in and walk out any time you want.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
